
|WKBSyntax: |YKBrecall

|YKOThe |YKBrecall|YKO command lets you beg the powers of Darkwind to
whisk you back to the center of town (COT) from anywhere in the
world that allows teleportation. After each successful use, the
powers must replenish for |YKB15 minutes|YKO before you can recall
again. You will be told when the cooldown has elapsed and recall
is available once more.

|WKBNotes:
|YKO    * Cannot be used if you are already at COT.
    * Cannot be used in rooms that block teleportation.
    * The 15-minute cooldown is independent of |YKBncot|YKO and any
      guild teleport abilities.
    * Newbies and applicants typically use |YKBncot|YKO instead, which
      has no cooldown.

